message.body: Did you say something to Victor?
I just wanted to clear something up.
Oh man, Taylor (Sam's brother's partner) passed away.
I didn't know until a few minutes ago because she posted about it on FB. I didn't get her text.
Yeah he died yesterday. Also, one of Eden's cats died today
I thought she said Monday? Wtf?? Which one?

Oh right Monday. Im loosing track of the days. And it was Ricky. I don't know if you remember. The black one. It's the one she had the longest. I was gonna call you tonight after work to tell you about both of them

Oh shit...how is she doing? I don't know if I should call because I know she sleeps early. I remember Ricky. it's the one i keep thinking it's a male but is actualky female. I talked to Sam, she said the funeral is next Saturday. Don't know if she would like company, so I said we could talk about that later.
Well Eden's at work tonight. She was really upset and it sucks she had a shift tonight.
And yeah i don't know about details yet but I plan on going
